31
00:03:52,650 --> 00:03:52,980
Dito.

32
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:53,920
Sanlai.

33
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:56,600
Gusto ko yung ibigay sa akin ni Jin Zhao.

34
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:01,960
May lason ba ang meatball ko o ano?

35
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,560
Sige, hindi ko maintindihan. Sige na.

36
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:16,839
Mum, uminom ka.

37
00:04:17,910 --> 00:04:18,680
Baliw.

38
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,709
Baliw ka ba talaga?

39
00:04:21,230 --> 00:04:22,029
Nandito na si Brandy,

40
00:04:22,029 --> 00:04:23,360
at hinikayat mo si Jiang Mu na uminom?

41
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:26,160
-Tama.
-Inumin mo na lang ang buong bote.

42
00:04:26,930 --> 00:04:27,830
Samahan mo akong uminom kahit isang beses.

43
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:28,710
-Sige.
-Samahan mo akong uminom.

44
00:04:28,710 --> 00:04:29,910
Tatapusin ko ang akin.
Tulungan ninyo ang inyong mga sarili.

45
00:04:29,910 --> 00:04:30,860
Tara, uminom tayo. Tara na.

46
00:04:30,860 --> 00:04:32,520
Jiang Mu,
gusto mo bang uminom?

47
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:33,320
Soda, pakiusap.

48
00:04:33,590 --> 00:04:34,640
Gusto mo ba ng yelo?

49
00:04:36,590 --> 00:04:38,710
Sige, may iba pa ba kayong mga kahilingan?

50
00:04:39,710 --> 00:04:41,740
Gusto kong kunin ni Jin Zhao ang inumin ko.

51
00:04:41,980 --> 00:04:42,500
Sige.

52
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:44,030
-Tara na, cheers.
-Tara na.

53
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,030
Kaya ako lang mag-isa ang umiinom?

54
00:04:46,030 --> 00:04:46,760
Sayang naman.

55
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,020
Sige, sige.

56
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,230
Brandy,

57
00:05:10,550 --> 00:05:12,310
Gusto ko rin ng malamig na inumin!

58
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,000
Sinuri ko

59
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:26,200
ang Pag-aagawan para sa iyo.

60
00:05:26,470 --> 00:05:28,800
Ang mga magsasaka ng prutas sa malapit
ang may gawa noon.

61
00:05:29,470 --> 00:05:31,470
Nagwisik sila ng tubig sa riles.

62
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,890
Sinabi nilang kumuha sila ng pera mula kay Wan Dayong.

63
00:05:41,150 --> 00:05:41,880
Ayos lang.

64
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,820
Alam niya ang lahat.

65
00:05:45,230 --> 00:05:46,880
Sa nakaraang Scramble,

66
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,470
