67
00:05:51,150 --> 00:05:52,150
Nabigador?

68
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,200
Sa,

69
00:05:54,710 --> 00:05:56,390
Alam mo ba kung ano ang isang navigator?

70
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,520
