-Anong klaseng dula 'yan?
-Alam ko na.

83
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:37,150
-At ginampanan mo ang Two of Bamboos.
-Kong the Two of Bamboos.

84
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:38,420
